I bought the DVD and I like it pretty good. A sunny day and families out on a beach frolicking. Pret teens to adults playing in the Surf and sand. Some distance shots but a few close up views. Picture quality an 8 on one to ten rating system. I seen the title listed in a Amazon.com kindle book titled, The Definitive Guide To Girls In Coming Of Age Movies by Carl Wo.
